title: The One About Drag Families
description:
Want to see the full episodes first? Head over to www.patreon.com/siblingrivalrypodcast to be the first to see our latest Sibling Rivalry Podcast Videos! This week Miz Cracker is filling in for Monét while she's busy being a winner of RuPaul's Drag Race All Stars! Filmed in April - Bob and Cracker discuss the (then very relevant) burning of Notre Dame and discuss their drag families. Starring: @BobTheDragQueen @MizCracker With executive producer @MitchFerrino --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/siblingrvalry/support
